可以使用您拨出的皮克敏来寻找宝藏，包括蛋糕和橡皮鸭。您甚至会在屏幕上看到他们给您带来这些宝藏。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/b2bb57d0-4bb5-11ee-bbfb-309e11cce1b0" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/b2bb57d0-4bb5-11ee-bbfb-309e11cce1b0" style="height:800px;width:480px;" alt="红色皮克敏叠加在键盘上。" data-uuid="48d303c2-88d4-3656-b522-531923042348"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">皮克敏探测器</div></figure><p>要玩游戏，您可以通过移动浏览器访问其<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://pikmin-finder.nintendo.net/">网站</a>，然后开始在手机上捕捉皮克敏。您还可以扫描在桌面浏览器上打开网站时显示的二维码。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/nintendos-new-mobile-game-lets-you-pluck-pikmin-on-your-browser-064423362.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/nintendos-new-mobile-game-lets-you-pluck-pikmin-on-your-browser-064423362.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> ce7445db-6d28-444a-8b98-b1d51cdc7302</guid><dc:creator>玛丽埃拉·穆恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 05 Sep 2023 06:44:23 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693896245</ingested><modified> 2023-09-05T06:44:09+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Utility Industry]]></category><category><![CDATA[Personal Finance - Career & Education]]></category><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Handheld & Connected Devices]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mariella Moon]]></category><media:content height="720" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/83803990-4bb0-11ee-bf6d-199b1c5976db" width="1280"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><