ybodys-gone-to-the-rapture-trailer-song.html"><em><ins>每个人都沉浸在狂喜</ins></em></a>之中<em>&nbsp;</em> The Chinese Room 工作室正在开发 2004 年原版 RPG 的续作<em>。《血族 2》</em>预计将于 2024 年秋季推出。</p><p> Chinese Room 保留了一些原始概念，同时抛弃了其他概念，以自己的愿景重新构建<em>《血统 2》</em> 。现代西雅图的场景以及 Hardsuit 的一些关卡和艺术设计都得以保留。然而，创意总监 Alex Skidmore 告诉<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.pcgamer.com/vampire-the-masquerade-bloodlines-2-has-been-quietly-rebuilt-by-dear-esther-developer-the-chinese-room-with-different-gameplay-mechanics-and-rpg-systems/"><em><ins>PC Gamer</ins></em></a> ，该游戏现在拥有“一个具有不同游戏机制和 RPG 系统的新代码库。”你将扮演一个年长的吸血鬼，而不是你<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2014-11-24-ccp-games-kills-a-fan-remake-of-vampire-the-masquerade-bloodl.html"><ins>在原版游戏中</ins></a>可能熟悉的新鲜面孔。虽然主角已经停滞了一段时间，所以你会和他们同时适应寒冷的环境。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="6f61d3d840d24f438f93917cfbcb205b"><div style="left:0;width:100%;height:0;position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/2clSTM3UvTo?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></div><p>对于 The Chinese Room 来说，这是一种新的挑战，到目前为止，The Chinese Room 一直专注于充满神秘感的大气步行模拟器，正如<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.polygon.com/23858293/perhaps-vampire-the-masquerade-bloodlines-2-release-date-developer-the-chinese-room"><em><ins>Polygon</ins></em></a>所言<em>&nbsp;</em>笔记。 <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/vampire-the-masquerade-bloodlines-2-delayed-2021-200243795.html"><ins>就像它的最新项目一样，</ins></a>该工作室多年来也经历了自己的麻烦。 2017 年，由于资金问题，该公司<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2017-09-24-everybodys-gone-to-the-rapture-creator-goes-dark.html"><ins>几乎完全关闭</ins></a>，后来 Sumo Digital 接手并重振了它（Sumo Digital 本身后来<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tencent-sumo-acquisition-091425058.html"><ins>找到了新的所有者，即腾讯</ins></a>）。</p><p>在接下来的几个月里，我们将进一步了解 The Chinese Room 为粉丝们准备的内容。 Paradox 计划在一月份更深入地讨论<em>《吸血鬼：避世血统 2》</em> 。 </p><div id="946bc5f1956341c7813e01154950499b"><div style="left:0;width:100%;height:0;position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/D6b6LGubq6I?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></div><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/vampire-the-masquerade---bloodlines-2-returns-from-the-shadows-with-a-new-developer-200008403.html?src =rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/vampire-the-masquerade---bloodlines-2-returns-from-the-shadows-with-a-new-developer-200008403.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 85cea5bc-5ffe-49aa-91ba-0b4a11924115</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Mon, 04 Sep 2023 20:00:08 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693856416</ingested><modified> 2023-09-04T19:40:20+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Personal Investing Ideas & Strategies]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/c744a000-4b59-11ee-92bd-ae17a3d99cbe" width="1920"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/c744a000-4b59-11ee-92bd-ae17a3d99cbe" width="1920"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></m