ion 和 PC 上提供。 <em>《最终幻想 16》</em>实现同样跨平台飞跃的前景令人着迷。</p><p>与此同时，吉田宣布为 PS5 玩家免费更新游戏。新功能<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/finalfantasyxvi/status/1698185605270691885"><ins>包括</ins></a>额外的角色皮肤、洋葱剑、更多控制器选项和幻化功能（即能够将克莱夫的剑的外观更改为其库存中任何其他剑的外观，而不影响统计数据）。该补丁现已可用。 </p><div id="05a8827b30a745389110aa8d170fc910"><div style="left:0;width:100%;height:0;position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/40ivdiYRu7A?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></div><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/final-fantasy-xvi-is-coming-to-pc-square-enix-confirms-190034778.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/final-fantasy-xvi-is-coming-to-pc-square-enix-confirms-190034778.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 5d65e581-a6b7-47ed-a212-1b67e7439680</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Mon, 04 Sep 2023 19:00:34 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693851162</ingested><modified> 2023-09-04T18:12:45+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="1350" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/1ec89190-4b4d-11ee-afff-335ece9a0500" width="2400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1350" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-up