dcasts-to-save-money-065639545.html">最近有消息称</a>，该公司考虑将这些类型的播客从其平台上完全撤下，因为它们会导致其年毛利润减少 3800 万美元。</p><p>报告称，大使广告在白噪音播客上效果不佳，因为听众通常不像对话或叙事播客那样投入。据报道，据说他们是更被动的听众，他们为了背景噪音而播放这些节目，因此 Spotify 并没有从这些广告中看到太多好处。</p><p>白噪音播客的制作者仍然可以通过听众的直接支持、付费会员资格和自动广告来赚钱。但此举正在切断一个重要的收入来源。另一方面，对于那些只想听叽叽喳喳的鸟儿或雷暴雨而不被推广<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/anchor/">Spotify 播客工具</a>之类的人打扰的听众来说，这可能是有益的。</p><p>此外，Spotify还提高了大使广告的资格门槛。播客现在需要在 60 天内拥有 1,000 名唯一听众（之前为 100 名）才能参与该计划。</p><p>该公司还计划邀请更多播客加入其自动广告计划。 Spotify 表示，它将与播客运营商将这些广告的收入分成两半，一改之前根据展示次数支付统一费率的做法。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/spotify-reportedly-locks-white-noise-podcasters-out-of-an-ad-program-150124532.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/spotify-reportedly-locks-white-noise-podcasters-out-of-an-ad-program-150124532.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 02a5dc2d-fc74-4c49-ab5e-1fbc4a044b8c</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Mon, 04 Sep 2023 15:01:24 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693903850</ingested><modified> 2023-09-05T08:50:59+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="3840" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/94653c40-4b30-11ee-ad5f-9c4d529acd74" width="5760"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3840" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/94653c40-4b30-11ee-ad5f-9c4d529acd74" width="5760"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ASSOCIATED PRESS]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[FILE - In this Tuesday, April 3, 2018 file photo, a trading post sports the Spotify logo on the floor of the New York Stock Exchange. U.K. regulators are stepping up scrutiny of the country's music streaming market to see whether there's enough competition, after lawmakers outlined concerns that big online major platforms like Spotify may be too dominant. The U.K.'s competition watchdog said Tuesday, Oct. 19 2021 it will carry out a “market study” to assess whether fresh measures are needed to improve streaming competition. (AP Photo/Richard Drew, File)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Britain Music Streaming]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Volkswagen will produce an EV version of its GTI hot hatch]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>大众汽车的 ID 产品线目前已经相当充实，包括从 ID.2all 紧凑型到 ID.4 跨界车等各种车型，但热销车型在哪里呢？大众汽车通过 ID.GTI 概念车<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.volkswagen-newsroom.com/en/press-releases/sporty-electric-emotive-volkswagen-presents-the-id-gti-concept-show-car-17584">回答了这个问题</a>，这是一款最终将投入生产的电动掀背车。</p><p>就像启发它的原始 GTI 一样（“I”不再代表喷射，而是“智能”），它是一款运动型、紧凑型掀背车，看起来静止不动。从尺寸来看，它比现款高尔夫 GTI 更短但更高，内部空间也稍大一些。 ID.GTI 基于（并且非常相似） <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/vws-id2all-compact-ev-will-cost-under-25000-when-it-arrives-in-2025-194635462.html">ID.2all 紧凑型</a>，增加了 20 英寸车轮、前、侧和后扰流板、后扩散器、蜂窝格栅、条纹图形、LED 雾灯等功能。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/6dd5e520-4b08-11ee-863e-a23359fc4b38" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/6dd5e520-4b08-11ee-863e-a23359fc4b38" style="height:675px;width:1200px;" alt="大众汽车将生产 GTI 掀背车的 EV 版本" data-uuid="9d542444-2c26-3611-ac6f-cb2f553bf4e6"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">大众汽车</div></figure><p>它还将进行操控和性能调整，但大众没有提供任何细节。 ID.2all 配备 223HP 电机，可在 7 秒内加速 62MPH，预计续航里程为 280 英里。不过，ID.GTI 很可能轻松击败这些数字，而且最高速度也应该更快。</p><p>大众确实表示 ID.GTI 将配备电子控制前轴差速锁，提供牵引力控制，就像当前的高尔夫 GTI 一样。该公司写道，它的工作效果会更好，“因为与任何电力系统一样，电力驱动电机的设置几乎可以无限变化。”由于电池位于车辆地板中，它的重心也较低，有助于操控。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/091ed060-4b08-11ee-bdbf-ccade7db78ce" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/091ed060-4b08-11ee-bdbf-ccade7db78ce" style="height:1010px;width:1795px;" alt="大众 ID.GTI" data-uuid="21a9fb43-2ea0-395a-baf5-beae9a3f37b4"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">大众汽车</div></figure><p>ID.GTI概念车的内部配备了格子呢运动座椅、驱动选择器、运动型方向盘、10.9英寸仪表盘以及12.9英寸信息娱乐系统。它还配备了 AR 平视显示器，可为驾驶员和前排乘客投影速度甚至轨道布局等信息。特殊的 GTI 按钮可激活红色照明方案。</p><p>大众表示将生产 ID.GTI 概念车，但没有透露何时或售价如何。不过，它很有可能会与 ID.2all 大约同时上市，ID.2all 的售价低于 30,000 美元，预计于 2025 年发布。 </p><div id="59ef90f6d04a420ab6e7423c761052d9"><div style="left:0;width:100%;height:0;position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/bMERyOqUpNA?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></div><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/volkswagen-will-product-an-ev-version-of-its-gti-hot-hatch-130029312.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/volkswagen-will-produce-an-ev-version-of-its-gti-hot-hatch-130029312.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 20f5421f-8c33-4389-a423-87f6af134984</guid><dc:creator>史蒂夫·登特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Mon, 04 Sep 2023 13:00:29 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693821518</ingested><modified> 2023-09-04T09:58:42+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Autos]]></category><category><![CDATA[Transportation]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Steve Dent]]></category><media:content height="1197" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/d0ee5eb0-4b00-11ee-b79d-3c3929b1290a" width="1795"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1197" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/d0ee5eb0-4b00-11ee-b79d-3c3929b1290a" width="1795"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[IvoHercik.com for VW]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Volkswagen will produce an EV version of its GTI hot hatch]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Volkswagen will produce an EV version of its GTI hot hatch]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA['Pizza Tower' is the 'Wario Land' + 'Sonic' crossover I didn’t know I wanted]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> 2023 年我最喜欢的电子游戏是，一位肥胖、秃顶的披萨厨师名叫 Peppino Spaghetti，他爬上一座中世纪的塔楼，击败了一个有感知能力的漂浮馅饼，威胁要炸毁他的披萨店。它是由一家名为 Tour de Pizza 的小型独立工作室开发的，由一位名叫 McPig 的设计师领导。它的配乐<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.pcgamer.com/2023s-best-gaming-soundtrack-was-co-created-by-a-high-school-student-and-a-first-time-composer/">主要由一位初次作曲家和一位高中生创作</a>。它的艺术风格既富有表现力又怪诞。它的名字叫<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2231450/Pizza_Tower/"><em>《Pizza Tower》</em></a> ，说实话，它是我长期以来玩过的最好的 2D 平台游戏之一。</p><p>我来晚了，因为<em>《Pizza Tower》</em>一月份登陆了 PC。目前，它在 Steam 上的所有 2023 年版本中拥有<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://steamdb.info/stats/gameratings/2023/">第二高的用户评分</a>。描述它的最简单的方式就是称其为现代<em>《瓦里奥大陆》</em> ——实际上，游戏的结构直接来自<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wario_Land_4"><em>《瓦里奥大陆 4》</em></a> 。几乎所有 20 个阶段都分为两半。在第一个游戏中，你可以悠闲地感受一切，收集<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://pizzatower.fandom.com/wiki/Toppins">披萨配料小伙伴</a>，解锁宝藏并寻找秘密房间。有一个评分系统，根据你完成关卡的速度和彻底程度而定——但佩皮诺不会死，而且你<em>不需要达到</em>一定的分数才能通过，所以你可以随意鲁莽地行动。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>然后是“<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://pizzatower.fandom.com/wiki/Pizza_Time">披萨时间</a>”。每个关卡的尽头都有一根柱子，一旦被推倒，整个关卡就会开始自行倒塌。音乐响起，计时器出现。这是在暗示你<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rDSoDDx-GTI">快点</a>离开那里。然而，你不能就这么原路返回；原始路径的部分内容被封锁，而某些秘密只有在疯狂冲回时才可以访问。如果未能及时到达入口，真正被诅咒的<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://pizzatower.fandom.com/wiki/Pizzaface">披萨脸</a>就会追捕你。这是一种简单的动力，好奇心被焦虑所逆转，但它一直对我有用。每个<em>披萨塔</em>阶段都以<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G8ihqJ15kao"><em>超级银河战士</em>的结局结束</a>，只有你扮演一个有趣的披萨店员，用<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://pizzatower.fandom.com/wiki/Forknight">叉子运送奶酪球</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://pizzatower.fandom.com/wiki/Pepperoni_Goblin">意大利辣香肠妖精</a>。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/f5699af0-40f8-11ee-afff-9e72b02be16d" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/f5699af0-40f8-11ee-afff-9e72b02be16d" style="height:1080px;width:1920px;" alt="PC 版视频游戏《披萨塔》的屏幕截图。" data-uuid="304fde90-76e8-328b-a80e-08a42f598fe0"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">比萨之旅</div></figure><p>然而，吸引我的不仅仅是它的结构，还有它的速度以及它的部署方式。事实上，我认为<em>《披萨塔》</em>相当于<em>《瓦里奥乐园》和</em><em>《刺猬索尼克》的</em>复兴版。快速解释：我不喜欢<em>索尼克</em>。当我五岁的时候，我在我姨婆的世嘉创世纪上玩<em>《刺猬索尼克 3》</em>时失败了，而在去年又对最初的五款游戏进行了一次震动之后，今天我也没有这样做。如果你这样做我明白了。但对我来说，<em>索尼克</em>提供的只是一种<a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://tevisthompson.com/sonic-and-tension/">糟糕的紧张感</a>，一种我无法触及的痒感。索尼克<em>可以</em>走得很快，但他的世界却阻碍了他的前进。<a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N6tSowlt7E4">绿山地带</a>的开阔田野最终被缓慢移动的平台、难以阻挡的岩架和令人窒息的水所取代。当我停下来时，需要几个节拍才能再次加速。持续浏览各个阶段的唯一方法就是记住它们。</p><p>另一方面， <em>Pizza Tower</em>确切地知道它是什么。佩皮诺的移动就像<a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Speed_(1994_film)"><em>《生死时速》</em></a>中的公共汽车一样，冲破墙壁并消灭挡在他路上的大多数敌人。当你冲刺时，他的双腿像轮子一样旋转，他的身体会发出彩色的光芒。当你改变方向时，听起来就像汽车的尖叫声。当你进行超级跳跃时，佩皮诺会无限地飞向空中。这个小家伙把自己打得精疲力尽，肚子先撞到砖头上，然后撞进了死胡同。这是一种持续的动态刺激，这是我想要从任何平台游戏中得到的那种。就像马里奥的轻快跳跃或大金刚的重击一样，佩皮诺的失控火车冲刺感觉明显是他自己的。</p><p>关键是你实际上有空间来探索这种运动形式。佩皮诺不会死这一事实发挥了重要作用——更少的恐惧鼓励更少的犹豫。除此之外，它只需要一秒钟就可以加速，而缩小的相机给你足够的时间来看到即将发生的事情。至关重要的是，控制很简单。只需按一下按钮即可进行墙跑、墙跳和潜入壁架下。 <em>《披萨塔》</em>为您提供了一系列精确的动作，但它更多的是建立在本能之上，而不是记忆之上。它知道它部分是一款赛车游戏，而不仅仅是一款平台游戏。事实上，要在一个赛段中获得最高排名，您必须完成“<a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://pizzatower.fandom.com/wiki/Pizza_Portal">第 2 圈</a>”。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/4452de60-40f9-11ee-8ffb-0aae9c169600" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/4452de60-40f9-11ee-8ffb-0aae9c169600" style="height:1080px;width:1920px;" alt="PC 版视频游戏《披萨塔》的屏幕截图。" data-uuid="98db4688-6752-370e-bdaf-af05eebf9e1c"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">比萨之旅</div></figure><p><em>Pizza Tower</em>令人振奋的动力足以让我喜欢它。但让我喜欢它的是它像任天堂一样致力于探索新的能力和感觉。前一刻你正踩着一匹<a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://pizzatower.fandom.com/wiki/Transformations#weenie_mount">热狗马</a>，下一刻你就变成了一个松散漂浮的幽灵，然后你就停下来打一场扭曲的高尔夫球（<a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cwssRkU415E"><em>瓦里奥</em>点头</a>）。重要的是， <em>Pizza Tower</em>会小心翼翼地在这些想法完成后将其<em>丢弃</em>。有时，它会引入一个机制，只是为了在同一关卡的后半部分颠覆它。</p><p> <em>Pizza Tower</em>的一切都增添了其独特的个性。这种艺术风格看起来就像是你在吃完肉食爱好者的披萨并在<em>Rocko&#39;s Modern Life</em>马拉松比赛中入睡后所做的一个梦。佩皮诺是一个现实的角色，害怕和愤怒，纯粹是通过令人回味的动画和动作。<a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1" href="https://ronandecastel.bandcamp.com/album/pizza-tower-soundtrack">令人难以置信的配乐</a>既<a data-i13n="cpos:19;pos:1" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mHRK28L5EeQ">时髦</a><a data-i13n="cpos:20;pos:1" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fnmHssx4lrE">又</a><a data-i13n="cpos:21;pos:1" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyIYD4JDLfQ">激烈</a>，本身就是对 Dreamcast 时代世嘉的回归，但又<a data-i13n="cpos:22;pos:1" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mYworLucNrY">完全是自己的</a>。这一切都很有趣！不仅体现在其自然的肢体喜剧中，还体现在它的笑话中——在玩这款游戏之前，你并没有真正讨厌<a data-i13n="cpos:23;pos:1" href="https://pizzatower.fandom.com/wiki/The_Noise">The Noid</a> 。</p><p>我什至没有谈论老板的战斗（诚实的决斗，达到“艰难但公平”的平衡）或结局（我玩过的最激烈和宣泄的序列之一）或令人惊叹的<a data-i13n="cpos:24;pos:1" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4BL_4oNwWo4&amp;t=4s">战争</a>。但我最后想说的是<em>，《披萨塔》</em>是制作致敬游戏的典范。它的灵感一目了然，但它并没有重述过去。相反，Tour de Pizza 思考了如何点燃经典精神，同时使其更原始、更活泼、更精神错乱。每年，我都会看到人们对经过焦点测试的大片和纯粹的模仿项目趋之若鹜。<em>披萨塔</em>的惊心动魄的狂野拒绝了他们——它只能是它本身。</p><p><core-commerce id="69389d6cfa3246da8ae7f77c4d3ff5ab" data-type="product-list"></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/pizza-tower-is-the-wario-land--sonic-crossover-i-didnt-know-i-wanted-130022186.html?src= RSS]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/pizza-tower-is-the-wario-land--sonic-crossover-i-didnt-know-i-wanted-130022186.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> c5825e4c-51a1-41ae-9f2c-95989afa141e</guid><dc:creator>杰夫·邓恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Mon, 04 Sep 2023 13:00:22 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693429625</ingested><modified> 2023-08-30T21:07:18+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jeff Dunn]]></category><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/23a3b630-40f9-11ee-82fc-50fb41901f6b" width="1920"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/23a3b630-40f9-11ee-82fc-50fb41901f6b" width="1920"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Tour de Pizza]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A screenshot depicting a boss fight in the video game Pizza Tower for PCs.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Pizza Tower]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[BMW's 'Vision Neue Klasse' concept teases high-efficiency EVs]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>宝马正在继续探索扩大的电动汽车产品线，发布了其最新概念设计<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.bmwusanews.com/newsrelease.do?id=4233&amp;mid=1">Vision Neue Klasse</a> 。该车型建立在 2021 年的 i Vision Circular 概念车和今年的<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/bmw-i-vision-dee-concept-digitizes-the-driving-experience-unveiling-first-look-ces2023-041555994.html">i Vision Dee 概念车的</a>基础上。除了值得讨论的美学特征之外，宝马还特别声称其 Vision Neue Klasse 的续航里程和充电速度将增加 30%，效率将提高 25%。 </p><div id="8bf0d3887cc248108d7629716e129131"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Z1LTr6frDS4?si=d60z6720cmWfjDVe" title="YouTube 视频播放器" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>该公司显然希望其<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/bmw-reveals-three-new-evs-for-its-summer-2023-lineup-210725344.html">新款电动汽车</a>能够真正区别于以前的车型。宝马管理委员会成员弗兰克·韦伯表示：“凭借 Neue Klasse，我们开始了公司历史上最大的投资。我们不仅在书写宝马的新篇章，而且在书写一本全新的书。”负责开发的AG在一份声明中表示。宝马声称其新设计“非常先进”，乍一看，你可能会认为该公司超越了一款车型。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/bmws-new-panoramic-vision-will-put-a-full-width-display-on-ev-windscreens-103515430.html">BMW Vision Neue Klasse</a>更有趣的功能之一包括充满活力的黄色休闲座椅。虽然它们看起来确实很有趣，但它们不太可能出现在任何即将上市的模型中。然而，理论上，去除铬和皮革应该会使整个生产更加环保。内饰还配备了新一代 iDrive 和 BMW 全景视觉系统。后者在前挡风玻璃底部提供导航、速度和歌曲等信息。</p><p>这家汽车制造商显然希望确保你看到这款概念车时除了幸福之外别无其他感觉，将外部油漆称为“欢乐明亮”。尽管该公司表示，这种颜色展示了“BMW Vision Neue Klasse 友好、面向未来的个性”，但我们不禁认为这听起来像是对季节性情感障碍 (SAD) 灯的描述。无论哪种情况， <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/bmw-confirms-the-i5-sedan-will-be-its-first-all-electric-5-series-vehicle-094954587.html">BMW</a> Vision Neue Klasse都会在慕尼黑举行的IAA Mobility 2023国际汽车展上首次公开亮相，但要到2025年才会上市。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/bmws-vision-neue-klasse-concept-teases-high-efficiency-evs-120045748.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/bmws-vision-neue-klasse-concept-teases-high-efficiency-evs-120045748.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 9e1d36b0-a053-4349-95c4-3336b2ccac2e</guid><dc:creator>萨拉·菲尔丁</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Mon, 04 Sep 2023 12:00:45 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693837635</ingested><modified> 2023-09-04T14:27:18+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Transportation]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Sarah Fielding]]></category><media:content height="2638" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/04958d00-4b2f-11ee-a0df-5532ed758b48" width="4000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2638" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/04958d00-4b2f-11ee-a0df-5532ed758b48" width="4000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[BMW]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A white BMW is on a gravel path with steps on one side and grass on the other.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[BMW 'Vision Neue Klasse' concept]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The Morning After: Facebook may offer paid ad-free plans in Europe]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>你愿意为 Facebook 付费吗？据<em>《纽约时报》报道，Meta 可能会为欧洲用户添加 Instagram 和 Facebook 的付费订阅选项。</em>无广告层解决了欧盟 (EU) 法规的问题，这些法规削弱了 Meta 一些最有利可图的数据收集方法，但《<em>纽约时报》</em>表示，该公司将继续在欧盟提供免费的 Facebook 和 Instagram 的广告支持版本。那么，这是一个节省成本的举措吗？无广告网站会影响公司的利润吗？早在四月份，Meta 就表示，欧盟的广告收入占公司总收入的 10%。</p><p> 5 月份，Meta 因将欧盟公民的数据转移到美国服务器而被欧盟罚款 12 亿欧元。此外，该公司因未能阻止数百万 Facebook 用户的手机号码（和其他数据）被抓取并发布到网上，于 2022 年被罚款 2.65 亿欧元。</p><p>哦，还有自我推销时间：《The Morning After》每周都会在 YouTube 上播出。它让我面对摄像机和本周最大的新闻。 I&#39;ll run through the most intriguing stories and tech launches of the last seven days – and say what I really think about them. You can watch, like, subscribe, share and abuse me in the comments ( <strong>don&#39;t</strong> do that) <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FmzB1sFPV0c&amp;ab_channel=Engadget">right here</a> .</p><p></p><p> All with no paid subscription option.至少现在还没有。</p><p> – Mat Smith</p><p></p><p>​​ <em>You can get these reports delivered daily direct to your inbox.</em> <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/about/newsletter/"><em>Subscribe right here!</em></a>​​</p><h3> The biggest stories you might have missed</h3><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/lenovo-yoga-book-9i-review-the-world-isnt-ready-for-dual-screen-laptops-but-lenovo-is-163009289.html">Lenovo Yoga Book 9i review: The world isn&#39;t ready for dual-screen laptops, but Lenovo is</a></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/xbox-series-s-is-now-available-in-carbon-black-with-1tb-of-storage-180602071.html">Xbox Series S is now available in Carbon Black with 1TB of storage</a></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/hitting-the-books-doom-guy-john-romero-abrams-press-143005383.html">Hitting the Books: The programming trick that gave us Doom multiplayer</a></p><p></p><h2> <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/engadget-podcast-iphone-15-event-preview-apple-rumors-123041285.html">Engadget Podcast: iPhone 15 event preview</a></h2><h3> With Bloomberg&#39;s Mark Gurman.</h3> <a href="https://www.engadget.com/engadget-podcast-iphone-15-event-preview-apple-rumors-123041285.html"><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/5fceaf70-4b03-11ee-b9f1-2c5d6075ad6b" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/5fceaf70-4b03-11ee-b9f1-2c5d6075ad6b" style="height:303px;width:675px;" alt="TMA" data-uuid="77124c28-1c68-31a3-8e2c-3cc7018b59ec"><figcaption></figcaption> <div class="photo-credit">Engadget</div></figure></a><p> This week, Devindra and Cherlynn are joined by <em>Bloomberg</em> ’s Mark Gurman, the purveyor of many Apple rumors that usually come home to roost. They discuss what we expect from the iPhone 15 and iPhone 15 Pro. Based on Gurman&#39;s reporting so far, the iPhone 15 will likely get Apple&#39;s Dynamic Island. The iPhone 15 Pro will gain thinner bezels, a titanium frame and a periscope camera could appear on the Pro Max. Oh, and there&#39;s the whole USB-C thing.</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/engadget-podcast-iphone-15-event-preview-apple-rumors-123041285.html"><strong>Continue reading.</strong></a></p><p></p><h2> <a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/powerwash-simulator-will-let-you-clean-the-grime-away-from-back-to-the-futures-delorean-141050171.html">&#39;PowerWash Simulator&#39; will let you clean the grime away from Back to the Future&#39;s DeLorean</a></h2><h3> Another crossover universe in need of a clean. </h3><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/5fceaf70-4b03-11ee-af77-1d497e665400" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/5fceaf70-4b03-11ee-af77-1d497e665400" style="height:380px;width:675px;" alt="TMA" data-uuid="d428ff2f-9007-345e-9877-bdbae808c686"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> Square Enix</div></figure><p> A Back to the Future expansion is on the way to <em>PowerWash Simulator,</em> a self-explanatory game that turned out to be one of 2022&#39;s biggest surprise hits. It&#39;s the game&#39;s latest crossover, following <a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/final-fantasy-viis-midgar-is-the-latest-grimy-locale-coming-to-powerwash-simulator-180930515.html"><em>Final Fantasy VII</em></a> , <em>Tomb Raider</em> and <em>SpongeBob SquarePants DLC</em> .</p><p> Alongside the DeLorean, you can also clean Doc Brown&#39;s van, the Hill Valley clocktower, the Holomax Theatre and the Time Train, from the less-good <em>Back To The Future 3</em> .</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/powerwash-simulator-will-let-you-clean-the-grime-away-from-back-to-the-futures-delorean-141050171.html"><strong>Continue reading.</strong></a></p><p></p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><h2> <a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-best-labor-day-2023-tech-sales-we-can-find-160000523.html">The best Labor Day tech sales we can find</a></h2><h3> Including deals on the MacBook Air, Hisense TVs and Solo Stove fire pits.</h3><h3></h3><p> Labor Day weekend isn&#39;t known as an especially fruitful time for tech deals, but there are a few notable discounts. Both the 13- and 15-inch versions of Apple&#39;s M2 MacBook Air are down to all-time lows, for one, as are Hisense&#39;s well-reviewed U6K and U8K TVs. If you&#39;re looking for the latest tech, the new Beats Studio Buds + are $40 off at the moment, too.</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-best-labor-day-2023-tech-sales-we-can-find-160000523.html"><strong>Continue reading.</strong></a></p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-facebook-may-offer-paid-ad-free-plans-in-europe-111508855.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-facebook-may-offer-paid-ad-free-plans-in-europe-111508855.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> d71d6bbb-adfa-41a2-b919-0e231495e6a0</guid><dc:creator> Mat Smith</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher> Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Mon, 04 Sep 2023 11:15:08 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693825266</ingested><modified> 2023-09-04T11:01:14+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mat Smith]]></category><media:content height="2876" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-05/35a3bee0-f935-11ed-9e4d-3e826c4a255a" width="4314"><media:keywords> headline </media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2876" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-05/35a3bee0-f935-11ed-9e4d-3e826c4a255a" width="4314"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:id